headline: 1 Vanguard ETF I'm Buying in 2025 and Holding Forever
summary: The right investment has the power to transform your portfolio, and exchange-traded funds (ETFs) can be a smart way to supercharge your savings with very little effort.  An ETF is a group of securities bundled together into a single investment.  Each fund can contain dozens or hundreds of stocks, and by investing in just one share of an ETF, you'll instantly own a stake in all the companies within that fund.

headline: 2 AI Robotics Stocks to Buy Before They Soar 185% and 315%, According to Wall Street Experts
summary: Jensen Huang is the CEO of Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA), a company whose chips power the vast majority of artificial intelligence (AI) systems.  Elon Musk, CEO of Tesla (NASDAQ: TSLA), made a related prediction last year: "I think by 2040, probably there are more humanoid robots than there are people."  With that in mind, Citigroup analysts estimate humanoid robot sales will hit $14 billion by 2030, $1.1 trillion by 2040, and $7 trillion by 2050.
